<body>
  <div id="carouselExampleIndicators" class="carousel slide" data-ride="carousel">
    <ol class="carousel-indicators">
      <li data-target="#carouselExampleIndicators" data-slide-to="0" class="active"></li>
      <li data-target="#carouselExampleIndicators" data-slide-to="1"></li>
      <li data-target="#carouselExampleIndicators" data-slide-to="2"></li>
    </ol>
    <div class="carousel-inner">
      <div class="carousel-item active">
        <img style="object-fit: cover" width="100%" height="100%", style="background-image: linear-gradient(rgba(0,0,0,0.5),rgba(0,0,0,0.5)), url(https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1426523038054-a260f3ef5bc9?ixid=MXwxMjA3fDB8MHxwaG90by1wYWdlfHx8fGVufDB8fHw%3D&ixlib=rb-1.2.1&auto=format&fit=crop&w=2832&q=80)" aria-hidden="true" preserveAspectRatio="xMidYMid slice" focusable="false">
        <div class="carousel-caption d-none d-md-block">
          <h1 class="shadowed"><strong>SuitsYou</strong> doesn't make you a <strong>CEO</strong> but it sure<strong> does help you look like one</strong>!</h1>
          <p class="shadowed">Change your life by discovering the countless styles you can try.</p>
          <p><%= link_to 'Browse Suits', suits_path, class: "btn btn-primary btn-lg" %></p>
        </div>
      </div>
       
      <div class="carousel-item">
      <img style="object-fit: cover" width="100%" height="600px" object-fit="cover" src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1425421669292-0c3da3b8f529?ixid=MXwxMjA3fDB8MHxwaG90by1wYWdlfHx8fGVufDB8fHw%3D&ixlib=rb-1.2.1&auto=format&fit=crop&w=1349&q=80" aria-hidden="true" preserveAspectRatio="xMidYMid slice" focusable="false">
        <div class="carousel-caption d-none d-md-block">
          <h1 class="text-left"><strong>Snap backs</strong> and tattoos?<strong> No Honey.</strong> Good job and <strong>nice suits</strong>!</h1>
          <p>Log in to begin your journey.</p>
          <%= link_to 'Login', new_user_session_path, class: "btn btn-primary btn-lg" %>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="carousel-item">
        <img style="object-fit: cover" width="100%" height="600px" src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1611943574626-91c9be96abc6?ixid=MXwxMjA3fDB8MHxwaG90by1wYWdlfHx8fGVufDB8fHw%3D&ixlib=rb-1.2.1&auto=format&fit=crop&w=1218&q=80" aria-hidden="true" preserveAspectRatio="xMidYMid slice" focusable="false">
        <div class="carousel-caption d-none d-md-block">
          <h1><strong>Dress</strong> like you're going<strong>somewhere better later</strong>!</h1>
          <p>Start right now by booking a suit with us.</p>
          <%= link_to 'Book a suit', new_user_session_path, class: "btn btn-primary btn-lg" %>
        </div>
      </div>
      </div>
        <a class="carousel-control-prev" href="#carouselExampleIndicators" role="button" data-slide="prev">
          <span class="carousel-control-prev-icon" aria-hidden="true"></span>
          <span class="sr-only">Previous</span>
       </a>
      <a class="carousel-control-next" href="#carouselExampleIndicators" role="button" data-slide="next">
        <span class="carousel-control-next-icon" aria-hidden="true"></span>
        <span class="sr-only">Next</span>
      </a>
  </div>
  <div class="container marketing">

    <!-- Three columns of text below the carousel -->
    <div class="row">
      <div class="col-lg-4">
        <img class="bd-placeholder-img rounded-circle" style="object-fit: cover" width="140" height="140" src="https://webstockreview.net/images/1-clipart-transparent-2.png" role="img" aria-label="Placeholder: 140x140" preserveAspectRatio="xMidYMid slice" focusable="false"><title>Placeholder</title>

        <h2>Browse</h2>
        <p>Find  your dream suit</p>
        <p><%= link_to 'View details', suits_path, class: "btn btn-secondary" %></p>
      </div><!-- /.col-lg-4 -->
      <div class="col-lg-4">
        <img class="bd-placeholder-img rounded-circle" style="object-fit: cover" width="140" height="140" src="https://i.imgur.com/FL0SG2s.png" role="img" aria-label="Placeholder: 140x140" preserveAspectRatio="xMidYMid slice" focusable="false"><title>Placeholder</title>

        <h2>Sign up</h2>
        <p>Create an account on SuitsYou</p>
        <p><%= link_to 'View details', suits_path, class: "btn btn-secondary"%></p>
      </div><!-- /.col-lg-4 -->
      <div class="col-lg-4">
        <img class="bd-placeholder-img rounded-circle" style="object-fit: cover" width="140" height="140" src="https://toppng.com/uploads/preview/white-number-3-in-orange-circle-11552783230zi7ci6abv7.png" role="img" aria-label="Placeholder: 140x140" preserveAspectRatio="xMidYMid slice" focusable="false"><title>Placeholder</title>

        <h2>Book</h2>
        <p>Pay and reserve it with just one click</p>
        <p><%= link_to 'View details', suits_path, class: "btn btn-secondary"%></p>
      </div><!-- /.col-lg-4 -->
    </div><!-- /.row -->

    <hr class="featurette-divider">

    <div class="row featurette">
      <div class="col-md-7">
        <h2 class="featurette-heading">It made me feel very confident and presentable. <span class="text-muted">It has made my day.</span></h2>
        <p class="lead">“I don’t wear suits very often but thanks to SuitsYou I managed to rent one for a job interview. It made me feel very confident and presentable.  Highly recommend if you don’t want to spend money on something you only wear once.”</p>
      </div>
      <div class="col-md-5">
        <img class="bd-placeholder-img bd-placeholder-img-lg featurette-image img-fluid mx-auto" width="500" height="500" src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1558222218-b7b54eede3f3?ixlib=rb-1.2.1&ixid=MXwxMjA3fDB8MHxwaG90by1wYWdlfHx8fGVufDB8fHw%3D&auto=format&fit=crop&w=634&q=80" role="img" aria-label="Placeholder: 500x500" preserveAspectRatio="xMidYMid slice" focusable="false">
      </div>
    </div>

    <hr class="featurette-divider">

    <div class="row featurette">
      <div class="col-md-7 order-md-2">
        <h2 class="featurette-heading">Oh yeah, it’s that good. <span class="text-muted">See for yourself.</span></h2>
        <p class="lead">“ 2 weeks ago I met with a new investor to talk about my new business. The meeting was so last minute that I didn’t have time to go and look for a new suit. Luckily, a friend recommended SuitsYou and in less than 2h I managed to find something, book it and have it delivered to my front door. And guess what? I managed to convince the investor my idea would be profitable and he’s on board. Thank you SuitsYou for such a great and quick service!”</p>
      </div>
      <div class="col-md-5 order-md-1">
        <img class="bd-placeholder-img bd-placeholder-img-lg featurette-image img-fluid mx-auto" width="500" height="500" src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1521341057461-6eb5f40b07ab?ixid=MXwxMjA3fDB8MHxwaG90by1wYWdlfHx8fGVufDB8fHw%3D&ixlib=rb-1.2.1&auto=format&fit=crop&w=634&q=80" role="img" aria-label="Placeholder: 500x500" preserveAspectRatio="xMidYMid slice" focusable="false">
      </div>
    </div>

    <hr class="featurette-divider">

    <div class="row featurette">
      <div class="col-md-7">
        <h2 class="featurette-heading">Such a clever idea! <span class="text-muted">Checkmate.</span></h2>
        <p class="lead">“I was meeting this girl at my favourite restaurant and as first impression matters, especially on your first date, I really needed something to show my style and possibly get her attention. Safe to say I never looked better! I’ve become addicted to this website as you never run out of choices.  Such a clever idea!”</p>
      </div>
      <div class="col-md-5">
        <img class="bd-placeholder-img bd-placeholder-img-lg featurette-image img-fluid mx-auto" width="500" height="500" src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1599557755020-56b2cd6d2d6b?ixid=MXwxMjA3fDB8MHxwaG90by1wYWdlfHx8fGVufDB8fHw%3D&ixlib=rb-1.2.1&auto=format&fit=crop&w=700&q=80" role="img" aria-label="Placeholder: 500x500" preserveAspectRatio="xMidYMid slice" focusable="false">
      </div>
    </div>

    <hr class="featurette-divider">
  </div>
</body>
